14CF360 & 15CF320 & 15CF426 - Defendant Edward T. Linn in court, in custody with attorney Jason Carlos Gonzalez (360 & 426 cases) and Atty Luchsinger (320 case).  Yolanda J. Tienstra appeared for the State of Wisconsin. Court reviews rights, charges and penalties. Victim rights compliance. Def enters NC plea to Ct 1 & 2 in 14CF360 and NC to Ct 1 in 15CF320. Court accepts pleas; withholds finding of guilt on Ct 1 in 360 and places on DPA, finds guilty of other plead counts; all remaining counts are DRI. ADA Tienstra heard. Atty Luchsinger heard. Atty Gonzalez heard. Court heard and imposes sentence:

14CF360 - Ct 1 - DPA;

14CF360 Ct 2 - 
2 yrs probation w/h;
6 months DCJ w/h&t comm forthwith;
No contact with victim;
No unsupervised contact with any juvenile females;
Shall obtain GED/HSED;
Shall maintain full time employment/education;
AODA and follow through;
Absolute Sobriety;
No Bars/Taverns/Liquor Stores etc;
Court does NOT put on sex offender registry at this time;
Costs;

15CF320 Ct 1 - 
Costs paid to the Clerk of Courts within 60 days unless a payment plan is established.
